{"tid":1444944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打政府唔入既話 就要打其他目標","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:20:41.000Z","uid":128594,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1dcdf992de63a9a068a64d942e3cf9798941aef","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"既然大陸死攬林奠既，我地就要由敵人內部開始分化<br />\n<br />\n大家宜家呢刻都比仇恨蒙蔽，將焦點放左落黑警到。但事實上，黑警就係體制內合法存在既團體，受到法律保護。只要一日港共當道，黑警都會無事<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但大家唔記得左係邊個掛住刷鞋而誤導政府，令到政府錯判形勢，導致送終亂局 - 係保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n邊個係615之後立刻同政府割席 - 係保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n邊個同元朗黑幫勾結 - 係保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n邊個同福建同鄉會有關係 - 係保皇黨</strong><br />\n<br />\n點解要攻擊保皇黨，因為議員係港共最唔容易控制既一環，會因為時局而出現變化。當初612，615之後，麥美娟爆林奠粗就真一大助證<br />\n<br />\n最理想緊係要保皇黨係選舉全敗，但臨近選舉個陣時國家機器一定會全力出動。所以宜家應該要向<strong>中間偏藍既市民帶出上面所講述既幾點，灌輸保皇黨為私利而賣港既想法，令到保皇黨長期受壓而向政府施壓。</strong><br />\n<br />\n做得保皇黨十個入面有八個都係為左利益，只要利益受損就一定會作反<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以搵多d由送終開始保皇黨賣港賣政府既證據，係各區大力宣傳。最緊要係多圖少字，要令三姑六婆都容易理解"},{"pid":"9ee8e67225f4b55c7fd30478173df48702032df9","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ad5ca43557520d21158f2d9c48d7b08b20464af","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3833558b9d6d81b521913011b0f9d01d8cf529a","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39f0448ea34a0ad6d9bc6a2d7ed5a41075c12bb5","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:58:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcedc8bed1e525ba0ff9250f7c9f6f38fef2161b","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5745881dce0310fc55f8de4c2390d059dfbb879","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:42:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c5b4b4b4f2874e03af3b9ec87a8e55ae276ac54","tid":1444944,"uid":148824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"急！禍必及妻兒！犬妻犬兒報料捉發完夢既手足！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c9e41e4559f9f4f05e546f409109132cd095e43b","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d265c9637e7fcb1f97c16aa7ad8103d4fd65c6ab","tid":1444944,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"【戰略】撳美金現金係最低成本嘅革命手段，成功嘅話無需攬炒，得中共自炒。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/adjxyRU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/adjxyRU</a>"},{"pid":"3d057190c072d6e96ee83e72c35bab7690ec7425","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"866769a50b37ba497dfd0cac0b064cf27e3edafd","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68ef8e6cc1c94e5b885ad07e58f132d9f67c165a","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fe2cd2f7889f677daeabe0ce6fe3bab42bf2a3d","tid":1444944,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:20:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}